OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FThree people have died in a suspected
OL,8,Foutbreak of hantavirus on a cruise
OL,9,Fship in the Atlantic Ocean, the World
OL,10,FHealth Organisation (WHO) has said.
OL,12,FThe WHO said one case of hantavirus
OL,13,Finfection has been confirmed, and
OL,14,Fthere are five additional suspected
OL,15,Fcases.
OL,17,FSouth Africa's Department of Health
OL,18,Fsaid a British passenger has tested
OL,19,Fpositive for hantavirus and is being
OL,20,Ftreated in intensive care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
