OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FITV News explains what hantavirus is
OL,8,Fand how it spreads.
OL,10,FWhat is hantavirus?
OL,12,FHantaviruses are a group of viruses
OL,13,Fthat are normally carried by rodents,
OL,14,Fsuch as rats, mice and voles.
OL,16,FThey are present throughout the world
OL,17,Fand can cause a range of diseases in
OL,18,Fhumans ranging from mild, flu-like
OL,19,Fillness to severe respiratory illness
OL,20,For haemorrhagic disease with kidney
OL,21,Fissues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
