OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FHow does it spread?
OL,9,FHantavirus is mainly spread by contact
OL,10,Fwith rodents or their urine, saliva or
OL,11,Fdroppings, particularly when the
OL,12,Fmaterial is disturbed and becomes
OL,13,Fairborne, posing risk of inhalation.
OL,15,FPeople are typically exposed to
OL,16,Fhantavirus around their homes, cabins
OL,17,For sheds, especially when cleaning out
OL,18,Fenclosed spaces with little
OL,19,Fventilation or exploring areas where
OL,20,Fthere are mouse droppings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
