OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FThe WHO says that while it rarely
OL,8,Fhappens, hantaviruses can also spread
OL,9,Fdirectly between people.
OL,11,FWhat are the symptoms?
OL,13,FSymptoms can include:
OL,15,FSymptoms of hantavirus pulmonary
OL,16,Fsyndrome usually show between one to
OL,17,Feight weeks after contact with an
OL,18,Finfected rodent. As the infection
OL,19,Fprogresses, patients might experience
OL,20,Ftightness in the chest, as the lungs
OL,21,Ffill with fluid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
