OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHow dangerous is it?
OL,14,FAn infection can rapidly progress and
OL,15,Fbecome life-threatening.
OL,17,FThe disease gained attention last year
OL,18,Fafter late actor Gene Hackman's wife,
OL,19,FBetsy Arakawa, died from a hantavirus
OL,20,Finfection in New Mexico.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
