OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FWhat is the cure?
OL,9,FThere is no specific treatment or
OL,10,Fcure, but early medical attention can
OL,11,Fincrease the chance of survival.
OL,13,FHow can you avoid hantavirus?
OL,15,FThe best way to avoid the germ is to
OL,16,Fminimise contact with rodents and
OL,17,Ftheir droppings, and using protective
OL,18,Fgloves and a bleach solution for
OL,19,Fcleaning up rodent droppings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
